channel.title: Oh my gosh (coincidence)
channel.description:
I was bored so i was typing random shit into google
type in
roflcoptorians
the thing that pops up is a j mod.
I know because vipsta was talking about a mod called mark and he posted and said roflcoptorians. and in his user info it has that he lives in cambridge and that he works for un undisclosed game company that he adores!!!!
